            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app>
                        <note xml:id="Job-018-fn1" type="footnote">JSul.I.04: The Karaim equivalent
                            of the standard Hebrew Job 18:1 is not included in the text, probably
                            intentionally, see Job 3:1, 4:1, etc. for similar cases. The text is
                            reconstructed here on the basis of Job 2:11 and ADub.III.84. The Hebrew
                            text is not omitted, see BHeb. <foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וַיַּעַן בִּלְדַּד הַשֻּׁחִי וַיֹאמַר </foreign>
                            ‘Then answered Bildad the Shuhite and said’ (Job 18:1). | C: <emph>Da
                                ǯoɣap berdi Bildad ol Šuḥly da ajtty</emph>. | QB: <emph>Da ǯoɣap
                                berdi Bildad ol Šuḥly da ajtty</emph>. | ADub.III.84: <emph>Da qaruv
                                berdi Bildad ol Šuvaḥly da ajtty</emph>. | Kobeckaitė (2019):
                                <emph>Da qaruv berdi Bildad ol Šuvaḥly da ajtty</emph>.</note>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
